1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:25,340 --> 00:00:30,020
[Phoenix Lands in the World]

3
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:34,500
[This story is purely fictional]

4
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,980
[Episode 10]

5
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,220
Ye Wuchen.

6
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:51,350
As I deleted you in the story,

7
00:00:51,870 --> 00:00:53,600
I was sent here as a punishment.

8
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:56,400
I can only use the Cloud Absorption Spell on you.

9
00:00:58,540 --> 00:00:59,970
Maybe this is fate.

10
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:03,010
We have to be tied together completely.

11
00:01:08,980 --> 00:01:09,940
How are you?

12
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:11,500
Does it still hurt?

13
00:01:12,470 --> 00:01:13,330
No, it doesn't.

14
00:01:22,490 --> 00:01:24,289
Why did you put everything away?

15
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:26,490
Do you regret marrying me?

16
00:01:28,870 --> 00:01:31,710
I think you're the one who should regret it.

17
00:01:33,580 --> 00:01:35,240
Did you look for me everywhere

18
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:36,670
and marry me

19
00:01:37,050 --> 00:01:38,410
just in order to kill me?

20
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,320
I just wanted to

21
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,229
test how sincere you were.

22
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,820
As you know,

23
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:50,289
the destiny of the women from our Moon Shadow Sect

24
00:01:50,289 --> 00:01:51,759
is all miserable.

25
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,960
I finally had the chance to get married.

26
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:56,430
I had to see

27
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,640
whether the groom

28
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:01,440
was worthy of being my lifelong partner.

29
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,050
How about you just leave

30
00:02:04,530 --> 00:02:05,670
after you recover?

31
00:02:05,810 --> 00:02:08,000
Just stay as far away from me as possible.

32
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,800
I won't leave.

33
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,080
This is my home.

34
00:02:10,990 --> 00:02:11,920
I'll leave then.

35
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:13,640
Come on.

36
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:15,660
Without me,

37
00:02:15,690 --> 00:02:18,150
the Cloud Absorption Spell will be useless.

38
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:19,120
Where can you go?

39
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:23,350
How do you know that?

40
00:02:25,130 --> 00:02:27,480
Aren't you afraid that I'll kill you again?

41
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,800
If you had really wanted to kill me,

42
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,030
you would have done it.

43
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:31,360
Would you have saved me?

44
00:02:34,250 --> 00:02:35,200
You're right.

45
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,760
Come to think of it,

46
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:40,090
after I go back, my client

47
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:42,320
will urge me to write novels every day.

48
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:43,910
I think this is good.

49
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,210
Your client?

50
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,150
It's like

51
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:49,310
the role of your master, Shangguan Ye.

52
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:52,930
Actually, at first,

53
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:54,230
in the version I wrote,

54
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:56,180
Ye Wuchen and Feng Nanxi

55
00:02:56,230 --> 00:02:59,560
were a perfect couple that everyone in the world would envy.

56
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,150
Unfortunately,

57
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:03,580
I don't know why it has been altered like this now.

58
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:05,350
A perfect couple?

59
00:03:07,790 --> 00:03:08,470
Forget it.

60
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:11,690
You won't understand even though I've explained it to you.

61
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:12,300
Ye Wuchen.

62
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,580
Just call me Shen Yu.

63
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,310
Since

64
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,790
Ye Wuchen and Feng Nanxi

65
00:03:17,230 --> 00:03:18,890
didn't be together in the end,

66
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,720
why don't you let me stay with you forever

67
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,320
with the identity of Shen Yu?

68
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:26,870
Don't you want the secret book anymore?

69
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:30,130
How can you explain it to your master if you don't kill me?

70
00:03:32,670 --> 00:03:35,440
Now you're the only one who believes in what Shangguan Ye said.

71
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,329
In my opinion,

72
00:03:36,350 --> 00:03:39,150
he just wants to take possession of the secret book privately.

73
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:41,280
Don't speak ill of my master like that.

74
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,770
Are you still angry?

75
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:58,890
No, I'm not.

76
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,920
You don't have to be so hard on yourself.

77
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:13,190
My master has done many things that hurt you.

78
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,390
It's reasonable that

79
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:15,770
you don't trust him.

80
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,149
[Secret Book of the Cloud Absorption Spell]

81
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,589
But I trust you.

82
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:25,370
If you had just wanted to steal the secret book,

83
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:26,440
when I got hurt,

84
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,280
you wouldn't have done that.

85
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,260
Besides,

86
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,870
I'm a she-devil.

87
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:36,030
Of course I have to keep my word.

88
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,830
Then where is the antidote?

89
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,200
It's here.

90
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:54,450
I lied to you. You believed it?

91
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:55,770
You lied to me?

92
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,100
Shen Yu.

93
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,600
Wait for me to come back.

94
00:06:04,370 --> 00:06:07,340
Why are you here instead of staying by

95
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,340
the she-devil's side to spy on her?

96
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:11,680
Master.

97
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:15,160
I've got the Secret Book of the Cloud Absorption Spell.

98
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,760
I was right about you indeed.

99
00:06:18,010 --> 00:06:19,190
I have a question.

100
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,080
Master,

101
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,300
why do you want this Secret Book of

102
00:06:23,410 --> 00:06:24,740
the Cloud Absorption Spell?

103
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:25,740
Of course my purpose is to

104
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:28,340
prevent this secret book from bringing disasters to the Martial Arts World again.

105
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:30,330
Since you've got it,

106
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:32,550
I'll no longer hold you responsible for the facts that

107
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:34,030
you hurt your fellow disciples

108
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:35,710
and saved the she-devil.

109
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:39,350
Next,

110
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:42,159
as long as you kill Feng Nanxi,

111
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:44,640
I'll allow you to join Zhouzong

112
00:06:44,890 --> 00:06:46,830
and restore your identity

113
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:49,260
as a legitimate member of the Xiaoyao Sect.

114
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,000
From my observation during these days,

115
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:54,110
compared with those righteous people,

116
00:06:54,110 --> 00:06:56,320
she has a stronger sense of justice and righteousness.

117
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,159
So,

118
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,010
killing the she-devil

119
00:06:59,010 --> 00:07:01,070
and eliminating the Moon Shadow Sect

120
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:02,790
should be reconsidered by us more carefully.

121
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:05,590
You've really been bewitched by that she-devil.

122
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:07,430
Master,

123
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,710
since I was a kid, you've taught me

124
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:10,440
to distinguish right from wrong

125
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,970
and think carefully before taking action.

126
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:13,700
Now that I'm confused about it,

127
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,050
I have to say it.

128
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:17,340
Master, please get rid of your prejudice

129
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:19,470
and stick to the principle of justice.

130
00:07:20,210 --> 00:07:21,140
How ridiculous!

131
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:23,470
How dare you question me and confuse right and wrong

132
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,670
because of that she-devil?

133
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:25,550
I dare not.

134
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:27,320
But I don't understand.

135
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:29,890
As members of a righteous sect,

136
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:31,430
we should educate and civilize all living creatures,

137
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:33,580
and guide the members of evil sects to the right path.

138
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:35,920
Since the Moon Shadow Sect has been disbanded,

139
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,400
and Feng Nanxi has lost her martial arts skills,

140
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,150
they won't be able to do evil things anymore.

141
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:41,000
Why do we still have to kill them all?

142
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,970
We must eliminate all the evil people.

143
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:45,270
Otherwise, there will be endless disasters in the future.

144
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:47,409
But you colluded with Ji Wuhuan, the chief guardian

145
00:07:47,409 --> 00:07:48,870
of the Moon Shadow Sect.

146
00:07:49,090 --> 00:07:50,970
Is that also considered as upholding justice?

147
00:07:50,970 --> 00:07:52,970
Why should we care about the means

148
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:55,420
while dealing with a she-devil like that?

149
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:56,810
I think

150
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:01,200
the difference between a righteous sect and an evil sect is that

151
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,590
we're prudent about what we should do and shouldn't do.

152
00:08:03,590 --> 00:08:06,660
You have no right to criticize me.

153
00:08:07,610 --> 00:08:09,930
Since Feng Nanxi has lost all her martial arts skills,

154
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:12,730
I can make other arrangements to assassinate her.

155
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,840
Since you're so stubborn,

156
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:19,170
just reflect on yourself on the Wuling Land.

157
00:08:19,650 --> 00:08:20,700
Without you,

158
00:08:20,770 --> 00:08:23,700
I don't think she can use the Cloud Absorption Spell.

159
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:45,450
Why hasn't he come back yet after such a long time?

160
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,020
I'm so bored alone.
